  "original_title": "\u0dc0\u0dd0\u0da9\u0db6\u0dbd\u0db1 \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0dbb\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0dca \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0db8\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0d82\u0dc4",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Acting President Ranil Wickramasinghe",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Speaker Mahinda Yapa Abeywardena said in a statement that the President had informed him that Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe had been appointed as Acting President.",
        "The announcement further states that the appointment was made in accordance with Article 37(1) of the Constitution with effect from today."
      ],
